            >
              <span>Visual SQL Builder for ClickHouse</span>
              <span class="text-indigo-600">No code required</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
              Build powerful dashboards with our visual query builder or
              leverage our TypeScript SDK. The easiest way to work with
              ClickHouse data.
            </p>
